data.description: MOVE-IN READY! Only a year old and shows brand new with a home warranty included. Discover peaceful countryside living at Liberty Village, offering a master-planned community of new homes designed exclusively for residents aged 55 and better. Short distance from State Road 200 and I-75, this community provides easy access to everything you need. Within minutes, you'll find top-tier hospitals, tons of shopping, dining options and nature attractions for the outdoor enthusiasts. This charming 2 Bed/2 Bath home boasts a spacious open design, optimizing every inch of interior space. A functional great room and dining room combo flow into an open concept kitchen space. The gourmet kitchen combines; stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, a table island with seating, and double walk-in pantry. The guest bedroom is situated off the foyer for ease and privacy, while the owner's suite is positioned toward the rear of the home, offering a secluded retreat. The study provides a versatile space, perfect for an office or craft/hobby room. Two car garage with new epoxy flooring and pull-down access ladder for extra storage. Additional features include; a transferable home warranty, paid HOA fees up to June 2024, irrigation system, new rain gutters and a covered lanai that overlooks a serene and private backyard with no rear neighbors. Community amenities include; pool with covered pavilion, pickleball, bocce ball, and shuffleboard coming Fall 2024. Low HOA fee $58.50 per month, and there are no CDD fees. Your peaceful and convenient lifestyle is waiting for you at Liberty Village. Start packing and make it your own!
